        {
            "id": 6435805,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Cadence設計系統(CDNS-US)大跌5.09%，報319.41美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Cadence設計系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDNS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDNS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDNS-US</a>)截至台北時間28日23:34股價下跌17.13美元，報319.41美元，跌幅5.09%，成交量2,245,283（股），盤中最高價338.55美元、最低價319.41美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.14%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.72%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.41%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-4.8%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Cadence設計系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDNS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDNS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDNS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.66%</li> <li>近 1 月：+23.83%</li> <li>近 3 月：+5.71%</li> <li>近 6 月：-4.23%</li> <li>今年以來：+7.67%</li></ul></section></main>",
