            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>帕卡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PCAR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PCAR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PCAR-US</a>)截至台北時間28日23:06股價下跌6.51美元，報120.69美元，跌幅5.12%，成交量1,542,692（股），盤中最高價128.30美元、最低價120.45美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.69%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.26%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-4.71%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>帕卡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PCAR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PCAR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PCAR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.87%</li> <li>近 1 月：+12.82%</li> <li>近 3 月：+5.29%</li> <li>近 6 月：+25.84%</li> <li>今年以來：+16.15%</li></ul></section></main>",
